    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of age and wear. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and minor dings, and the interior upholstery shows significant fading and some staining. Mechanically, it runs and drives, but the suspension is getting noisy and it will likely need new tires and a brake service in the near future. It\u2019s a solid choice for someone looking for a budget-friendly option who doesn't mind putting in a little work.",
